text: Kamoe peuleupah Bani Israi ‘Oh lheueh jititi laot nyang luah ‘Oh ka troh keunan bak saboh kaom Nyang seumah patong Tuhan jìpeugah Kheun kaom Musa teuma bak gopnyan Tanyoe pih meunan jinoe taseumah Tapeugot Tuhan jinoe keu kamoe Lagee awak nyan tuhan le leupah Musa kheun teuma jahe that gata Nyang kon-kon haba nyan dum tapeugah
